  "title": "Inheritance of albinism in certain interspecific and intersubspecific crosses in groundnut (Arachis hypogaea L.)",
  "abstract": "A study of the several interspecific and inter-subspecific crosses indicated that albinism in groundnut is recessive and in these crosses is controlled by triplicate recessive loci",
